</ul>

em 'btn[clk=$v+1]{$v doubled is $d}`v=0:+1;d=v*2`' NB. use `` for scripts; all vars that depend on referenced vars are auto updated
<script>let v = 0; let d = v * 2;</script>
<button click="() => v = v+1">{v} doubled is {d}</button>

